        "Id": "547f47bd-14fa-4f31-b950-b37e91f39ff5",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Window Shotter Clearance Sale",
        "Location": "LOCATION_WET_RAT",
        "PublicId": "130458220457",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/wet/scene_rat_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 629d88c1-3e7b-4d9f-b017-f082a6806c8f).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Our client, a guard within The Block, wishes to settle an argument he had with a co-worker about whether or not the windows were truly replaced with bullet proof glass, as their employer had insisted. As budget cuts have replaced all of their ammunition with nitroglycerine coated jelly beans, it is up to you to prove him right with your authentic bullets... And take out some disagreeable peers of his.",
